org.intellimate.izou.sdk.events

Class Event

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.intellimate.izou.sdk.events.Event
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventModel<Event>, Identifiable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EndedEvent, LeavingEvent, MuteEvent, PlayerCommand, PlayerError, PlayerUpdate, PresenceEvent, StartEvent, StartMusicRequest, StopEvent, StopMusic, UnMuteEvent

    public class Event
extends Object
implements EventModel<Event>
    This class represents an Event. This class is immutable! for every change it will return an new instance!
